  <Summary>Istvan is haunted by the ghost of Zenna Prohl who he accused of being a witch so he could get her land.

Two treasure hunters try to find a sunken galley but run into a ghostly galleon instead.

When Vincent Perrault disturbs an ancient burial ground for stones for his new house he awakens the curse of the screaming skulls.

Leftenant Jordan's ghost still flies the foggy skies over England looking for his landing strip.</Summary>
